Package com.mongodb.connection

Class ProxySettings

java.lang.Object
com.mongodb.connection.ProxySettings
@Immutable public final class ProxySettings extends Object
This setting is only applicable when communicating with a MongoDB server using the synchronous variant of MongoClient.

This setting is furthermore ignored if:

  • the communication is via Unix domain socket.
  • a TransportSettings is MongoClientSettings.Builder.transportSettings(TransportSettings) configured}.
Since:
4.11
